{"tid":2397420,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"土瓜灣瘋了","createTime":"2021-02-06T12:02:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-06T12:21:28.000Z","uid":344793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"44c014f032595eece8442d5436201512e2157ae3","tid":2397420,"uid":344793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T12:02:03.000Z","msg":".<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WrWG9a-HuJY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DWrWG9a-HuJY&d=ZxGTC5m4wH5D2fXTYNKMIQy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=0c62ef27\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WrWG9a-HuJY</a>"},{"pid":"072bf1b354f402728f0bb6167406779e6cec5014","tid":2397420,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T12:05:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e5e72e3a5b6d9b7f7ec25444216b21f104e7833","tid":2397420,"uid":344793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T12:10:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gBjW8ZD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgBjW8ZD.jpg&h=c3103c2c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f8cb600254c7aa80d99c87775c507d2e9949bb43","tid":2397420,"uid":344793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T12:11:23.000Z","msg":"政府今日（二月六日）引用《預防及控制疾病（對若干人士強制檢測）規例》（第599J章），作出限制與檢測宣告（下稱「相關宣告」），自下午八時起限制在土瓜灣指明「受限區域」（即<span class=\"blue\">土瓜灣馬坑涌道4-6號華發大廈</span>，見附件）內的人士（下稱受檢人士）須留在其處所並接受強制檢測。受檢人士須在其處所等候，直至區內所有已識別的受檢人士完成檢測，而相關檢測結果亦已獲大致確定，方可離開其處所。政府目標是在明日（二月七日）上午約七時左右完成此行動，以達致「同心抗疫，小區『清零』」的目標。<br />\n   <br />\n  政府發言人表示：「根據第599J章，政府可按防疫需要，作出限制與檢測宣告。由於土瓜灣馬坑涌道4-6號華發大廈近期出現確診個案，經評估後相關區域感染風險有機會較高，政府決定就相關區域作出限制與檢測宣告。」"},{"pid":"d3beb27fc9420b69fa0181a6358fe3dd6f6539e1","tid":2397420,"uid":344793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T12:12:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Heiheihits/videos/432571434753390\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHeiheihits%2Fvideos%2F432571434753390&d=ZxGTC5m4wH5D2fXTYNKMIQy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=c8fc6ee4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Heiheihits/videos/432571434753390</a>"},{"pid":"197e060d539c915fcfefba6f2d0196c65b91c754","tid":2397420,"uid":38777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T12:21:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}